# Sparse Checkout Configuration for Reference Models
#
# This file defines the recommended sparse checkout pattern when using
# kairos-reference-models as a Git submodule.
#
# To apply this configuration to a submodule, run:
#   git -C path/to/submodule sparse-checkout init --cone
#   git -C path/to/submodule sparse-checkout set ontologies mappings shapes examples
#
# Or copy this file to .git/info/sparse-checkout in the submodule's git directory
#
